## Deljeni scoping modul (Dev 1 vmesnik — UPORABI, ne podvajaj)
`const { requireOwnership, requireEnrollment, assertEnrollment, scopedListWhere,
isTrainingOwner, USER_ROLES, TRAINING_ROLES, RESOURCE_TYPES } = require("../middleware/scopeMiddleware");`
- `requireOwnership(type,{param})` — route middleware ZA requireRole; type ∈ training|topic|question|assessment|equivalenceGroup; tuj/neobstoječ → 404; ADMIN dovoljen le za "training".
- `requireEnrollment` — za /assessment-attempts/start; PUBLISHED + UserTraining(PARTICIPANT); ob uspehu `req.enrolledAssessment`.
- `assertEnrollment(userId, assessmentId)` — ista logika kot čista funkcija za klic v controllerju.
- `scopedListWhere(user, type)` — Prisma where fragment za findMany (INSTRUCTOR svoje; ADMIN `{}` le za "training", sicer `null` → seznam prepovedan/403).

## DEV 2 — Question bank (lastnik `types/models.ts`, publish-first)
Scope: odstranitev LearningObjective, `EquivalentQuestionGroup→EquivalenceGroup` (scope+cleanup),
odstranitev `reviewedById` (reviewedAt ostane). Podrobnosti v `brief-dev2.md`.
Zaščiti route (Dev 1 se jih ni dotaknil):
- `GET/PUT/DELETE /questions/:id`, `PATCH /questions/:id/status` → `requireRole("INSTRUCTOR")` + `requireOwnership("question")`
- `GET /questions` → `scopedListWhere(req.user,"question")` v controllerju
- `POST /questions` → v controllerju `isTrainingOwner` za `topic.trainingId` (404 za tuj)
- equivalence route → `requireOwnership("equivalenceGroup")` / `scopedListWhere(...,"equivalenceGroup")`
- **Umakni ADMIN iz `requireRole`** na question/equiv vsebinskih route (matrika: ADMIN ni content-collaborator).
Ne odstranjuj enum vrednosti. Objavi `types/models.ts` zgodaj.

## DEV 3 — Assessment / attempts / grading / pairing / analitika
Scope: pairing (`pairedAssessmentId`), enrollment guard na /start, grading endpoint +
SUBMITTED→GRADED + preračun score, by-LO → by-topic analitika, en-poskus (D). Podrobnosti v `brief-dev3.md`.
Čakaš na Dev 2 objavljen `types/models.ts` (equiv rename, LO removal).
Zaščiti route:
- `POST /assessment-attempts/start` → `requireEnrollment` (ali `assertEnrollment` v controllerju)
- `GET/PUT/DELETE /assessments/:id`, `PATCH /:id/status`, `GET /:id/results`, `POST /generate` → `requireOwnership("assessment")`
- `GET /assessments` → `scopedListWhere(...,"assessment")` za INSTRUCTOR; participant veja filtrira na vpisane treninge prek UserTraining
- analitika → `requireRole("INSTRUCTOR")` + scope (ADMIN nima instructor analitike)
- **Umakni ADMIN iz `requireRole`** na assessment/analytics vsebinskih route.

## Vrstni red
Dev 2 lahko starta takoj (uvozi scoping modul). Dev 3 starta, ko je Dev 2 objavil `types/models.ts`.
Oba se vračata v `feat/db-v2-dev1` (ali v phase0 integracijski branch — uskladi z vodjo).
